.shell powershell

alt + q                 : komorebic close
alt + w                 : komorebic minimize

# Move windows
alt + left              : komorebic move left
alt + down              : komorebic move down
alt + up                : komorebic move up
alt + right             : komorebic move right

# Manipulate windows
alt + f                 : komorebic toggle-float
alt + c                 : komorebic toggle-monocle

# Layouts
alt + x                 : komorebic flip-layout horizontal
alt + z                 : komorebic flip-layout vertical
